title: Is the Ace family getting evicted? Let’s talk about it
description:
Hello Fool Fam! This week on Fool Coverage, we spill the tea of what it's like to launch a makeup brand and what it takes to be a brand owner, as well as we cover some pop culture news such as Harry Jowsey's gay slur towards James Charles, the Ace family's mansion auction, Kourtney and Travis Barker engagement, and Manny tells a story of the worst makeup collab he's ever done!
Follow Laura on IG: @larlarlee
Follow Manny on IG: @mannymua733
